title: r/Entitledparents Doctor Kicks Entitled Mom Out Of Hospital!
description:
r/Entitledparents An entitled mother finds out the hard way that she can't already get what she wants! She comes into a hospital with her son, who had a boo-boo. Meanwhile, OP is a doctor who was dealing with actual life-or-death situations. When she demands that the doctor stops everything that he's doing to address her son, OP runs out of patience and has security kick her out of the hospital!
